<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880425-0044 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News: Bell Atlantic Corp. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> BEL WNEWS </CO><DATELINE> BELL ATLANTIC Corp. (Philadelphia)  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Bruce S. Gordon was named to the new position of vice president, marketing. He will coordinate Bell Atlantic's marketing activities and serve as marketing staff officer for each of the firm's telephone companies. He previously was vice president, sales, for Bell of Pennsylvania. </TEXT></DOC>